Reverse & Palindrome

In a given sentence, reverse each word and print the reversed words in the sentence. If there is a palindrome in the words, print
 those words. If there is no palindrome print “No palindrome”.

Sample Input1:

mom cooks yummy dish

Sample Output1:

mom skooc ymmuy hsid

mom

Sample Input2:

we seven eve madam

Sample Output2:

ew neves eve madam

eve

madam

Sample Input3:

java is a programming language

Sample Output3:

avaj si a gnimmargorp egaugnal

No palindrome

